GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 15b: Compensation Review and Approval Process for Officers and Key Employees
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: All board members are sent a questionnaire about the Executive Director's performance which is returned to the Board Chairman. The Executive Committee of the board uses these comments to prepare the annual review for the Executive Director.

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 12c: Explanation of Monitoring and Enforcement of Conflicts
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: Annually, each board member signs a conflict of interest policy statement.

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 11: Form 990 Review Process
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: Form 990 is reviewed by the Finance and Audit Committee before it is filed.

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 7a: How Members or Shareholders Elect Governing Body
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: Delegates to Augsburg vote and approve new board members at the annual meeting.
